---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Home"
  description="Eoin McAllister is an ML engineer building reinforcement learning systems, research prototypes, and production ML infrastructure."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Eoin McAllister</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">ML engineer building reinforcement learning systems and production ML software.</h1>
    <p class="hero-lead">
      I work across applied research and engineering: training agents, shaping experiments,
      and turning ML ideas into systems that are usable by teams.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/research" class="btn-primary">View research</a>
      <a href="/projects" class="btn-ghost">Browse projects</a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn-ghost">About me</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="highlights">
    <div class="highlight">
      <span class="highlight-label">Current focus</span>
      <p>Language-conditioned control for RL agents without retraining task-specific policies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight">
      <span class="highlight-label">What I build</span>
      <p>Research prototypes, evaluation tooling, shared RL infrastructure, and production-facing ML systems.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight">
      <span class="highlight-label">Background</span>
      <p>Based in Dublin. Previously Intel. Currently building at UrbanFox.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-kicker">Start here</p>
      <h2>Three fast ways to evaluate my work.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <a href="/research" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Research</span>
        <h3>What I’m investigating</h3>
        <p>Current RL directions, what problems I care about, and the kinds of systems questions I like to work on.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/projects" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Projects</span>
        <h3>Code you can inspect</h3>
        <p>Open-source repos from graylayer-labs, including shared RL infrastructure and supporting tooling.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/about" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">About</span>
        <h3>Experience and fit</h3>
        <p>Who I am, how I work, and the environments where I’m most effective as an ML engineer.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section proof">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-kicker">What matters</p>
      <h2>The through-line in my work is making ML ideas legible and shippable.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="proof-grid">
      <div class="proof-item">
        <h3>Research-minded engineering</h3>
        <p>I like problems that require both experimentation discipline and implementation depth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-item">
        <h3>Systems perspective</h3>
        <p>I care about training loops, evaluation, reproducibility, interfaces, and how other people use the system after the prototype works.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="proof-item">
        <h3>Clear communication</h3>
        <p>This site is where I’m collecting the projects, notes, and research threads that best represent how I think.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-page) 52px;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .section-kicker,
  .highlight-label,
  .card-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary,
  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    border: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-mid);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .highlights,
  .cards,
  .proof-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .highlights {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .highlight,
  .card,
  .proof-item {
    padding: 24px var(--space-page);
  }

  .highlight,
  .card {
    border-right: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .highlight:last-child,
  .card:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }

  .highlight p,
  .card p,
  .proof-item p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 52px 0 0;
  }

  .section-heading {
    padding: 0 var(--space-page) 22px;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .section-heading h2 {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .cards {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    transition: background 0.12s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    background: rgba(128, 128, 120, 0.04);
  }

  .card h3,
  .proof-item h3 {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .proof {
    padding-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .proof-grid {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .proof-item {
    border-right: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .proof-item:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .highlights,
    .cards,
    .proof-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .highlight,
    .card,
    .proof-item {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .highlights .highlight:last-child,
    .cards .card:last-child,
    .proof-grid .proof-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }
</style>
